quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  4,24,"E saЕӢiiЙ“e Й“en ka rewЙ“e, si wanaa Й“en Й“e jeyruЙ—on ka Гұaame mon. ЖҠum ko Farilla Alla e dow mooЙ—on. Daginanaama on ko woni Й“aawo Й“en Й—on, nde Й—aЙ“Й“itorЙ“e jawle mon hara ko on saЕӢiiЙ“e wanaa on jinndooЙ“e. Kala mo dakmitorЙ—on e maЙ“Й“e desal : jonniteeЙ“e teЕӢe maЙ“Й“e Й—en. Ko farilla. Bakkaatu fawaaki e fii ko yarlondirЙ—on e mun Й“aawo farilla on. Pellet, Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  4,25,"Kala e mooЙ—on mo hattaaaki feere resugol seЕӢiiЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e, ko [resugol] Й“en Й“e jeytirЙ—on Гұaame mon, immorde e curbaaЙ“e mon gomЙ—imЙ“e. Alla no Anndai gomЙ—inal mon ngal. Yoga e mon ko e yoga ResireeЙ“e duЕӢayee yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, jonniron Й“e teЕӢe maЙ“Й“e Й—en no moЖҙЖҙiri. SaЕӢiiЙ“e hara wanaa jinndooЙ“e njaatoo. Si Й“e seaЕӢike Й“e addii paЕӢkare, no fawii Й“e feccere ko fawii saЕӢiiЙ“e rimЙ“e Й“en e lepte. ЖҠum, ko fii on huluЙ—o e mo'on yanugol e jeeno. Ko nde muГұГұotoЙ—on Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on. Alla Haforoowo HinnotooЙ—o"
  4,26,"Allaahu On no Faandii ЖҒannginanngol on O Fewna on e laawi Й“eya adinooЙ“e on, O JaЙ“ana on tuubuubuyee. Alla ko AnnduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  4,27,"Alla no Faala nde O JaЙ“aЕӢta on tuubuubuyee, Й“en jokkuЙ“e mbeleeЙ—e faalaa nde ooГұorton ooГұannde mawnde"
  4,28,"Alla no YiЙ—i Hayfinanta on, neЙ—Й—aЕӢke tagaama ko o lo'uЙ—o"
  4,29,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, wata on Гұaamir jawle mon Й—en hakkunde mooЙ—on e mehre, si wanaa hara ko e njulaaku ngu welaЙ—on e muuЙ—um. Wata on waru pittaali mon Й—in. Pellet, Alla Laatike HinnotooЙ—o on"
  4,30,"kala huuwuЙ—o Й—um e hoore ngaynu e tooГұe, aray Men Naada mo yiite : Й—um laatike newaniiЙ—um Alla"
  4,31,"Si on woЙ—Й—itike [bakkaatu] mawЙ—i Й—i haЙ—aЙ—on Й—in e mun, Men Heefanay on boneeji mon Й—in, Men Naadira e naatirgal teddungal"
  4,32,"Wata on yelo ko Alla ЖҒurniri yoga e mon dow yoga. Hino woodani worЙ“e Й“en geЙ“al immorde e ko Й“e faggitii kon, hino woodani kadi rewbe begeЙ“al immorde e kon ko Й“e faggitii. Tororee Alla immorde e ЖҒural Makko. Pellet, Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o kala huunde"
  4,33,"Wonannde kala Men WaЙ—anii Й—um ronooЙ“e [heftuЙ“e] e Й—um ko jibimЙ“e Й“en acci, e Й“adondiraaЙ“e ; e Й“en Й“e ahodunoЙ—on e mun : jonneeЙ“e geЙ“al maЙ“Й“e ngal. Pellet, Alla Laatike ko O SeediiЙ—o e kala huunde"
  4,34,"WorЙ“e Й“en ko ГұiiЙ“uЙ“e [e daЕӢkiitagol] rewЙ“e Й“en, sabu ko Alla ЖҒurniri kon yoga maЙ“Й“e e hoore yoga, e sabu kon ko wintii e jawle maЙ“Й“e. [rewЙ“e] moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en, ko yaЕӢkiniiЙ“e reenotooЙ“e ka wirnii, sabu kon ko Alla Reenini Й“e.ЖҒen [rewЙ“e] Й“e huloton dartagol(cuwtagol) mun : waajeeЙ“e, feronЙ“e ka ndaЙ—Й—udiiji, piyonЙ“e. Si Й“e Й—oftike on, wata on aЙ“Й“ir e dow maЙ“Й“e laawol ! Pellet, Alla Laatike ToowuЙ—o, MawЙ—o"
  4,35,"Si on hulii lurral hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, imminee Гұaawoowo immorЙ—o ka yimЙ“e gorko on e Гұaawoowo immorЙ—o ka yimЙ“e debbo on. Si Й“e faandike moЖҙЖҙinngol, Alla Hawrindinay hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o, HumpitiiЙ—o"